content: "Paint a photorealistic portrait of a young woman standing on a mountaintop, looking out at a vast, sprawling cityscape below. The woman should be depicted with a determined expression on her face, with her fists clenched at her sides. Behind her, a bold, stylized sun should be rising over the horizon, casting a warm, golden light over the scene. Use advanced techniques such as lighting and shading to create a highly realistic image."
